ACTIVIST USE

This platform is specifically designed for disability rights activism and social
justice advocacy. We encourage its use for:
- Legitimate political advocacy
- Government accountability campaigns
- Disability rights organizing
- Workers' rights activism
- Public interest journalism
- Educational purposes

We explicitly discourage its use for:
- Harassment or threats against individuals
- Illegal activities
- Misinformation or conspiracy theories
- Hate speech or discrimination
- Violence or incitement to violence

---

PRIVACY COMMITMENT

This software is designed with privacy as a core principle:
- No user tracking or analytics (beyond basic Cloudflare security logs)
- No personal data collection
- No cookies for profiling or advertising
- No third-party tracking scripts

This commitment is binding on all forks and derivatives that use the
InjuredWorkersUnite name or brand.

